OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FITV News Entertainment Reporter Rishi
OL,8,FDava caught up with James McAvoy at
OL,9,Fthe premiere of his directorial debut,
OL,10,FCalifornia Schemin'
OL,12,FWith more than 20 awards to his name
OL,13,Fand about 50 films under his belt,
OL,14,FJames McAvoy has now stepped behind
OL,15,Fthe camera.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
