FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FBest known for his roles in X-Men, The
OL,8,FChronicles of Narnia, Atonement, The
OL,9,FLast King of Scotland...and my
OL,10,Fpersonal favourite Wanted, the 46-year-
OL,11,Fold has directed his first film
OL,12,FCalifornia Schemin'.
OL,14,FIt follows the steps to stardom of
OL,15,FSilibil N' Brains, a Dundee-based rap
OL,16,Fduo who pretended to be American in
OL,17,Forder to be taken seriously in the
OL,18,Fmusic industry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FYou're probably thinking, 'Who on
OL,8,FEarth thought of that storyline?'
OL,9,FWell, it is based on a true story.
OL,11,F"I had been looking for something that
OL,12,Ftold stories about people from lower-
OL,13,Fincome backgrounds, council estates,
OL,14,For as we call it in Scotland, council
OL,15,Fschemes," says the actor turned
OL,16,Fdirector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FMcAvoy and I are chatting at the
OL,8,Ffilm's premiere in London's Leicester
OL,9,FSquare, basking in the sunshine that
OL,10,Fflows through the cinema's giant
OL,11,Fwindows.
OL,13,F"A lot of the stuff I was reading was
OL,14,Fpretty grim", he says, "and a bit sort
OL,15,Fof gritty, award-worthy fair, which is
OL,16,Fgreat... I love those films, but that
OL,17,Fis not what I wanted to make."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,F"I wanted to make something that is
OL,8,Fstill entertaining, that is still
OL,9,Fadventurous, that is still cinematic,
OL,10,Fthat is still a mainstream popcorn
OL,11,Fmovie."
OL,13,FSilibil N' Brains consists of Gavin
OL,14,FBain and Billy Boyd. Bain is Brains
OL,15,Fand Boyd is Silibil. In the early 00s,
OL,16,Fthey were mocked and overlooked by the
OL,17,Fmusic community for sounding too
OL,18,FScottish.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FOne dismissive individual even
OL,8,Freferred to them as the 'rapping
OL,9,FProclaimers'.
OL,11,FDown but not out, the pair reinvented
OL,12,Fthemselves by adopting American
OL,13,Faccents and telling people they were
OL,14,Ffrom California, rather than Dundee.
OL,16,FIt worked! They signed a record deal,
OL,17,Fappeared on MTV and even performed on
OL,18,Fa UK tour with Eminem's group D12.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FGavin says, "It was like two and a
OL,8,Fhalf years as Silibil N' Brains, but I
OL,9,Fstayed in character for five years. I
OL,10,Fcame clean after five years. It was
OL,11,Fquite a journey. It became an identity
OL,12,Fcrisis. Some of the backstory bled
OL,13,Finto my real life."
OL,15,FSeamus McLean Ross, who plays Gavin/
OL,16,FBrains in the film, couldn't quite
OL,17,Fbelieve the tale when he first heard
OL,18,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,F"I was just so captivated by the
OL,8,Faudacity of it, the bravado and the
OL,9,Flust for life. Two young men with a
OL,10,Fmission, not knowing where they are
OL,11,Fgoing, just off the cuff, I love
OL,12,Fpeople like that."
OL,14,FBain wrote about their fakery in his
OL,15,F2010 memoir, California Schemin': How
OL,16,FTwo Lads from Scotland Conned the
OL,17,FMusic Industry.
OL,19,FThere was also a 2013 documentary
OL,20,Fabout the boys, called The Great Hip
OL,21,FHop Hoax.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FReflecting back on their musical
OL,8,Fmischief, Boyd says 'this was pre-
OL,9,Fsocial media, before the time of
OL,10,Fpeople creating art and putting it out
OL,11,Fthere within minutes."
OL,13,F"We couldn't do that back then.
OL,14,FNowadays, things would be different,
OL,15,Fyou can be more authentic and be
OL,16,Fyourself and have those opportunities
OL,17,Fthat we didn't have. You don't have to
OL,18,Fbreak down those boundaries as much."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
