PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FBorn in Glasgow, James McAvoy's career
OL,8,Fhas taken him to Hollywood, appearing
OL,9,Fon screens and garnering fans around
OL,10,Fthe world.
OL,12,FHe's not just directing California
OL,13,FSchemin', he stars in it too. It
OL,14,Fprovided him with a unique opportunity
OL,15,Fto actually use his own accent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,F"I think I've played five Scottish
OL,8,Fcharacters in 30 years," he recalls.
OL,9,F"Once I get over the bump of the first
OL,10,Fday of being like 'this feels weird',
OL,11,Fwhich is perverse, that speaking in my
OL,12,Fown accent when I'm getting paid
OL,13,Fshould feel weird, but that's just the
OL,14,Fway my career has gone."
OL,16,F"Once I get over that bump, it's kind
OL,17,Fof gorgeous and just feels very
OL,18,Fnatural."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1775830266
OL,3,CJames McAvoy 'wanted to make a popcorn
OL,4,Cmovie about people from council
OL,5,Cestates'
OL,7,FSmiling while reflecting on getting to
OL,8,Fwork with McAvoy, Samuel Bottomley -
OL,9,Fwho plays Billy/Silbil - said that
OL,10,F'it's such a good opportunity to stand
OL,11,Fon the shoulders of giants or in the
OL,12,Fshadow of a giant and watch how they
OL,13,Fwork. I feel very grateful for it."
OL,15,FThe film, which is out in cinemas on
OL,16,FFriday, April 10, is very much about
OL,17,Ffriendship, community and identity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
